<br />
( i mean 3 months as playing a baby dragon before you even get the chance to quest to become an adult dragon so you can fly and do some spells....oh yeah..only the dedicated become the dragons...which i so plan to be <img src="images/smiles/icon_twisted.gif" alt="Twisted Evil" border="0" />  )
