				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Kivahri Raynsmajic wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">how much does the game cost to play?
