<br />

<br />
Price is $12.95 per month.
<br />

<br />
Minimum Specs: 850 MHz or faster Pentium III or AMD Athlon processor, 256 MB or more RAM, 64 MB or greater supported Direct3D and Hardware Transform & Lighting capable video card, Direct X 8.1 or greater and a dial-up Internet connection.
<br />

<br />
Recommended Specs: 1.4 GHz Pentium IV or AMD Athlon processor, 512MB RAM, GeForce 3 or better, DirectX 8.1a, and a DSL or Cable modem Internet connection.
<br />

<br />
During beta on a dialup I had frequent crashes till the area was cached on my system, then it was fairly stable (For a Beta) and FPS were quite acceptable 15-40 depending on crowdedness. The footprint is about 600ish meg from what people are saying. I don't know what that entails though. I'm not technical in that aspect. =)
<br />

<br />
Near the end of the Beta my connection and loading ability was GREATLY improved.
<br />

<br />
The game is made so that "Casual" players can still play the game. Soloing is quite possible for anyone. Quests do not require camping, mobs do not drop items for the most part...
<br />

<br />
Of course, the more you play, the stronger you will be...<br />_________________<br /><div align=center><img src="http://www.eqbeastlord.com/~makani/Graphics/Makani.jpg" border="0"></img></div></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
